content: mgacek-blockydevs: Merged two significant PRs this month: #1826 "feat: add cosmos plugin" (+28,304/-20,580 lines) and #1934 "feat: improvements for plugin-cosmos" (+15,513/-12,371 lines), contributing substantial code changes across 87 files (+7,946/-3,936 lines).
